wiki.content: "Out From Under" was originally by artist Joanna for the Bratz movie. Britney's version was well-received by critics, with one reviewer referring to it as Spears' best ballad since "I'm Not a G irl, Not Yet a Woman". The song is believed to be about Spears' relationship with ex-husband Kevin Federline.
